  "handNote": {
    "lettering": "Regular and neat letters, thinly incised, all of equal height, and slightly variable width, without serifs. Alpha with broken bar, beta with closed loops (upper slightly smaller), Mu has full length slanting strokes; omicron full size; sigma has horizontal top and bottom, middle strokes taking the full width; rhomboid omega.",
